#doctrine[
  "The Ens manifests the highest initiatic virtue of the plant it is made from... The nature of spagyric tinctures, and in particular the Ens, is to clear out the blocks in our psychic makeup and anatomy, similar to what is called Nadis in yoga or the Meridians in acupuncture." — Mark Stavish, Practical Plant Alchemy, 1998
